Preamble:
The Broadly Relaxed User Handshake (BRUH) license embodies the spirit of broad freedom and minimal restriction. It aims to facilitate a relaxed, user-friendly environment for the usage, modification, distribution, and enjoyment of the licensed software. By utilizing the software under this license, you agree to the terms set forth herein, recognizing the laid-back nature of this agreement as a handshake between peers.

